folder: Lafayette Street & Washington Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
(1)
80 to 86 Laight Street, at, adjoining and west of the N.W. corner of Washington Street. Also shown is part of Nos. 416-424 Washington Street, a 5-story warehouse adjoining the N.W. corner of Laight Street.
July 16, 1932.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same several years later and showing the corner house (No. 80) occupied and improved.
August 2, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.
